<html>
<head>
    <title>Hey Buddy!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hey ${Name},</h1>
        <p>
            I just wanted to reach out and say hi! <br><br>
            I hope everything’s going well for you and that you’re finding time to relax and enjoy the little things.<br><br>
            It’s been a while since we last connected, and I thought of you today,
            so I figured I’d send a quick message your way.<br><br>
            Take care and hope to hear from you soon!
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>